elements.name: Login with valid user and email, then click in pages and only filters  the first option and second option

steps.name: I set scenario "Pages_filter_by_item_1st_to_4th" and version app "<VERSION>"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/pages/']"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-contentfilter-menu"
I click on element having css selector "li[data-option-index='4']"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-contentfilter-author"
I click on element having css selector "li[data-option-index='2']"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-contentfilter-tag"
I click on element having css selector "li[data-option-index='1']"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-contentfilter-sort"
I click on element having css selector "li[data-option-index='2']"
